<<> AzureBlade: Then, I think we should go back to Maximal City. They will 
> probably be able to help you find your activation code. However, it is 
> far away. Do you think you will be able to fly a long way?>>

wings out for flying...but they should work well enough, considering her size 
in relation to them. Hopefully they'd be good for long distances.
